    <item>
      <title>私募股权股份暴跌，因为特朗普关税眩晕市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/private-equity-shares-plunge-as-trump-tariffs-stun-world-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的全球关税震惊了全球市场，美国最大的私募股权公司的股票在周四下跌，其中一些股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/private-equity-shares-plunge-as-trump-tariffs-stun-world-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 17:29:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥股票的“毫发无损”的“无损”领先全球收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/-unscathed-from-tariffs-mexico-stocks-jump-most-in-the-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥的股票市场周四飙升最多，因为投资者堆积在此消息后，该国被排除在唐纳德·特朗普总统的计划之外，该计划将关税征收贸易伙伴的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/-unscathed-from-tariffs-mexico-stocks-jump-most-in-the-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 15:36:27 GMT</pubDate>
